{"id": 1107, "genre": 1001, "title": "陪人逛街需要具备哪些技术要素？ ", "description": "除了出钱出力以外，配逛街还需要掌握哪些技巧？（题图来自：Victor Beuren）", "record_count": 1744, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160710220840scqZAkSoPQ42dr0U.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-08-24T03:00:23Z", "options": [{"id": 110336, "content": "百般不愿藏于心\r\n笑容满面我愿意", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 480284}, {"id": 110337, "content": "显瘦！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 480284}, {"id": 110338, "content": "手机4G流量充足、电池电量保持良好状态", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 730137}, {"id": 113922, "content": "忍耐力:他人衣品low的时候，还是要保持围笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 748551}, {"id": 110339, "content": "活地图，良好的审美", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 730138}, {"id": 110340, "content": "化了妆逛街试啥都美，为了省钱，建议素颜?", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 151052}, {"id": 110341, "content": "一起逛街的两个人眼光要一致", "image": "img/option/option/201608241444051kG3JTLbMUFXyiCe.jpg", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 730144}, {"id": 110342, "content": "随机应变", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 730149}, {"id": 110343, "content": "随机应变", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 730149}, {"id": 110344, "content": "随机应变", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 730149}, {"id": 110345, "content": "陪她一起砍价", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 730149}, {"id": 110346, "content": "钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 730155}, {"id": 110347, "content": "男生表示真的很不理解为什么要走这么多店", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724620}, {"id": 110348, "content": "哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 730163}, {"id": 110349, "content": "脚力好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 730163}, {"id": 110350, "content": "耐心", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216219}, {"id": 110351, "content": "眼光", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 730176}, {"id": 110352, "content": "能拎包，能给建议，能出钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 601095}, {"id": 110353, "content": "唯一的技巧就是做好自己买更多的心理准备???", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671086}, {"id": 110354, "content": "好看，不贵，买！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 716297}, {"id": 110355, "content": "一无所获后的唠叨?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 728194}, {"id": 110356, "content": "准备好治疗纠结的心", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236751}, {"id": 110357, "content": "砍价太疼痛，心酸谁能懂", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 728413}, {"id": 110358, "content": "为什么要逛那么多家???", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719774}, {"id": 110359, "content": "出远门不常有，而逛街常有，也许能更加熟悉你所在的城市吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 695264}, {"id": 110360, "content": "耐心和热心", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 334929}, {"id": 110361, "content": "让场面不冷", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 665728}, {"id": 110362, "content": "能走能说，眼光要好，砍价一流。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 36446}, {"id": 110363, "content": "审美能力", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 123049}, {"id": 110619, "content": "陪她逛到爽", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 732127}, {"id": 110364, "content": "不玩手机 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 730223}, {"id": 110365, "content": "我爱你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 728665}, {"id": 110366, "content": "全能", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 683887}, {"id": 110367, "content": "能转，脚力好;有劲，提东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 722484}, {"id": 110368, "content": "能给建议不敷衍的明显", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714455}, {"id": 110369, "content": "在选择恐惧症时决绝的发表决定", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714455}, {"id": 128289, "content": "一个好肾", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814014}, {"id": 110370, "content": "体力，财力，审美能力", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 665043}, {"id": 110371, "content": "能在无聊中寻找乐趣的能力；能在众多难看的商品中挖掘它们优点的能力！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 676353}, {"id": 110372, "content": "敲边鼓引导好友到自己想逛地方的能力……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642769}, {"id": 110373, "content": "脚力体力?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 730331}, {"id": 110374, "content": "时刻保持微笑，主动付钱拿包包，及时提议去哪家特色店喝杯饮料", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 730343}, {"id": 110376, "content": "有钱才是硬道理", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 730351}, {"id": 110377, "content": "陪老婆逛街“必须”会反复重复——好看!", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 567112}, {"id": 110378, "content": "万金油，能聊天说地，还要颜值高！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725591}, {"id": 110379, "content": "好的耐力，好的臂力，帅气的面貌，温和的脾气，充足的现金，乖乖听话", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 710223}, {"id": 152364, "content": "不带眼睛不带耳朵不带智商", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898058}, {"id": 110380, "content": "大家说的对啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 301157}, {"id": 110381, "content": "自己调整好心情…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666762}, {"id": 110383, "content": "独立的贴合或高于买者的品位?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725485}]}